-Demo showing how to use rollbars log4j appender

-Steps to setup

-I use intellij but you can use whatever IDE you choose

-clone the project repo

git clone https://github.com/iflanagan/JavaLog4j2Demo.git

-Open the project in IDE

edit the log4j2.xml and add your rollbar token edit the helloWorldAction.java class and add your rollbar token

-build project

mvn clean install compile

-Run web server default port is 8080

mvn jetty:run

-open a web browser and got to the following url

http://localhost:8080/basic-struts/

enter in your name let the date auto populate and then click submit.
